      "reason": "A failure rate of 3-4 per minute stays below the alert threshold but accumulates 180-240 stuck orders per hour. The team would not be paged until the problem has been silently impacting customers for an extended period. Need a complementary alert on order state duration (orders stuck in PROCESSING > N minutes).",
      "routed_to": "Coach K"
    },
    {
      "type": "missing_observability",
      "issue": "Runbook is 18 months stale — on-call engineer has no trustworthy recovery procedures",
      "reason": "During a 3am incident with stuck orders, the engineer will open a runbook that may reference outdated states, deprecated error codes, or recovery steps that no longer work. A stale runbook is worse than no runbook because it gives false confidence. This must be updated and a review cadence established.",
      "routed_to": "Coach K"
    }
  ],

  "confidence": {
    "level": 55,
